high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to kitchen island
Pick up bread on kitchen island
Turn right, walk around chair, turn left, walk forward to refrigerator
Open refrigerator, place bread inside, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, remove bread, close refrigerator
Turn left, walk to end of counter, turn right at sink
anns.task_desc: Move bread from counter to refrigerator, followed by moving from refrigerator to counter

high_descs: Turn right to move to the kitchen island.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the island.
Turn right to move to the end of the island, and then head left to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge on the second shelf, close the door, and then open the door to remove after a few seconds.
Turn left and carry the bread to the sink.
Place the bread on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold loaf of bread on the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the counter.
Walk around the center table to face the fridge.
Cool the bread in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the bread on the corner of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To cool a loaf of bread as well as place it on the counter.
